quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  24,21,"Ko onon …ďen gom…óin…ďe, wata on jokku …óate Seytaane …óen, kala jokku…óo …óate Seytaane …óen, pellet, o yamiray [mo] ko boni kon e ko a√Īaa kon. Sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden; hay e gooto e moo…óon laa…ďataano poomaa, kono Alla hiMo la…ď…ďina on mo O Muuyi. Alla ko O Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  24,22,"Wata joomiraa…ďe …ďural ngal e yaajeende nden e moo…óon woondu wonndema …ďe okkortaa …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen e …ďillii…ďe …ďen e feru…ďe …ďen ka Laawol Alla, yo …ďe yaafo. Kaa on yi…óaa yo Alla yawtan on? Alla ko O Yawtoowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,23,"Pellet, …ďen wonu…ďe tukkude [sonnaa…ďe] saŇčii…ďe welsindii…ďe gom…óin…ďe, …ďe hu…óaama ka aduna e ka Laakara no woodani …ďe Lepte maw…óe"
  24,24,"√Ďalnde seedoytoo e dow ma…ď…ďe …óen…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e koy…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, ko …ďe laatinoo kon hi…ďe golla"
  24,25,"Nden √Ďalnde Alla huu…ďinanay …ďe [njo…ďdi] Diina ma…ď…ďe Goongaha kan, …ďe annda pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga ∆Āannguka kan"
  24,26,"Rew…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii wor…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen. Wor…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii rew…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen. Rew…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii wor…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen, wor…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii rew…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen. ∆Āee …óoo ko hisnaa…ďe e kon ko …ďe wowlata, no woodani …ďe haforaneede e arsike teddu…óo"
  24,27,"Ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe, wata on naatu e cuu…ói tanaa cuu…ói mo'on …óin haa duŇčino…óon salminon e dow yim…ďe majji …ďen, ko …óum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on. Bela jo'o onon on waajitoto"
  24,28,"Si on tawaali nder ton go…ó…óo, wata on naatu ton haa duŇčane…óon, si on wi'aama: \"Yiltee\" haray yiltee, ko …óum …ďuri laa…ďannde on. Alla non hiMo Anndi ko golloton kon"
  24,29,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde naatoton e cuu…ói …ói ho…óiraaka hara no e nder majji miranhoy mo'on, Alla non hiMo Anndi ko won…óon e fe√Ī√Īinde e ko won…óon e suu…óude"
  24,30,"Maakan wor…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen yo …ďe heltu ndar…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen …ďe reena farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin, ko …óum …ďurata la…ď…ďinnde …ďe. Pellet, Alla ko O Humpitii…óo ko …ďe huuwata"
  24,31,"Maakan rew…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen yo …ďe heltu ndar…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe reena farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin, wata …ďe fe√Ī√Īin cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe ndin si wanaa ko fee√Īi kon e mayri. Yo …ďe fawu tiggaaje ma…ď…ďe …óen ka becce ma…ď…ďe, wata …ďe fe√Ī√Īinan cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe ndin si wanaa genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen maa…óum baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa…óum baabiraa…ďe genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa…óum musi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe musi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe banndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum sonnaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum …ďen …ďe …ďe jeyiri √Īaame ma…ď…ďe maa…óum …ďen wor…ďe jokkoo…ďe …ďe haaju mun alaa e rew…ďe, maa…óum boobo mo ∆īellitaaki e awraaji sonnaa…ďe …ďen. Wata …ďe tappindir koy…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen fii yo Annde ko …ďe suu…ói kon immorde e cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe. Tuubee rutto…óon ka Alla on fow mo'on, ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe bela jo'o on malete"
  24,32,"Resinee …ďe resaali …ďen e moo…óon e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen immorde e muccu…ďe moo…óon e hor…ďe moo…óon, si …ďe laatike waasu…ďe Alla al…óinay …ďe immorde e ∆Āural Makko ngal, Alla ko O Yaaju…óo Anndu…óo"
  24,33,"∆Āe he…ďaali feere resugol …ďen yo …ďe habbo haa Alla al…óinira …ďe ∆Āural Makko ngal. ∆Āen wonu…ďe …óa…ď…ďude soottaade e …ďen …ďe √Īaame moo…óon jeyi, soottaadede …ďe si on anndii e ma…ď…ďe mo∆ī∆īere, jonnee …ďe immorde e jawdi Alla ndin, ndin ndi O jonni on, wata on waawnu hor…ďe moo…óon …ďen e fii jeeno, si …ďe faandike saŇčaade, wata on …óa…ď…ďu jawkal ngurndam aduna, kala waawnuu…óo …ďe pellet, Alla …ďaawo baawnugol …ďe ko O Surroowo Yurmitee…óo"
  24,34,"Gom…óii Men jippinii e moo…óon Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe e misal immorde e …ďeya wulinoo…ďe ko adii on e waaju wonannde huloo…ďe [Alla] …ďen"